{"id": 1427, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于职场礼节这件事，你有哪些拿不准的事情？", "description": "每次一不留神就得罪人的时候，才感受到大家对礼貌的定义是如此不同。（题图来自：Violeta Noy）", "record_count": 10420, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170104143606Wf1cZV4yKCqTYkXF.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-06T03:00:11Z", "options": [{"id": 152578, "content": "请客谁买单！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900574}, {"id": 151555, "content": "老师\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 854052}, {"id": 152324, "content": "作为新人，不善于沟通，慢热，怎么和同事相处", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898934}, {"id": 151301, "content": "不想加班怎么说？", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893741}, {"id": 151302, "content": "遇到简单的问题改不改问", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843464}, {"id": 151561, "content": "别人错的时候是不是就让他错下去，还是要体现情商优雅地暗示他？", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895285}, {"id": 151311, "content": "该不该否定领导的老旧错误思想", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893791}, {"id": 174096, "content": "朋友在老板发放的工作用ipad中的\r\n照片流里看到了老板和她老公的艳照\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956265}, {"id": 151314, "content": "如何礼貌地劝阻女同事撒娇", "image": null, "praise_count": 89, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668809}, {"id": 151827, "content": "开口应该说什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824600}, {"id": 151316, "content": "?这个表情在不同的年龄层有不同的区别", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 868356}, {"id": 151572, "content": "善心汇好看是好看，就是有点大", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895317}, {"id": 151828, "content": "经常快下班时经理走过来问，晚上加班吗？然后又说，晚上我恐怕要加班了！试问：我到底该不该下班？好烦⊙﹏⊙", "image": "img/option/option/20170108172312wreashmb17p8jHY2", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 866815}, {"id": 151574, "content": "善心汇扶贫济困，均富互生！在这里没有只有相互帮助！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895317}, {"id": 151831, "content": "记人的名字很难，有什么好的办法么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893768}, {"id": 178967, "content": "到底怎么解决", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971311}, {"id": 151320, "content": "怎么讨好自己的师傅", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893834}, {"id": 151321, "content": "阿猫阿狗都叫老师。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808640}, {"id": 151834, "content": "如何表达自己心中想要升职，表示一直在做吃力不讨好的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895384}, {"id": 151581, "content": "我也想知道怎么解决………\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895054}, {"id": 151837, "content": "应不应该和领导说玩笑话？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896914}, {"id": 152096, "content": "团队同事该如何管理？分寸如何拿捏更好？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897730}, {"id": 151329, "content": "被加派了超过职责的任务怎么办？", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835888}, {"id": 151586, "content": "和上级的关系熟点好还是生疏点好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853037}, {"id": 151587, "content": "怎样可以跟领导做到人的平等 职位的尊重\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849166}, {"id": 151332, "content": "如何面对莫名其妙讨厌我的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 152101, "content": "如何正确判断出出老板说的话的真正含义", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898105}, {"id": 151334, "content": "关于称呼，我们不管男女都叫某工。哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605975}, {"id": 151335, "content": "总忍不住多管闲事怎么破", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893861}, {"id": 151336, "content": "用OA网上协同办公，文字交流的时候到底要商务还是亲切，一句话是不是不加表情都不好意思发，结尾一定要用“～”吗？比较难为人的请求一定要用?表情表达自己也没办法这时老板的意思么?", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256663}, {"id": 151592, "content": "如何与领导相处", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895438}, {"id": 151848, "content": "如何跟自恋且装逼而且老是打扰别人工作的人共处？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819941}, {"id": 153384, "content": "该怎么巧妙的拒绝领导？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903546}, {"id": 151337, "content": "微信就不是用来谈工作的！！微信不是用来谈工作的！！微信不是谈工作的！！！！！！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891637}, {"id": 151593, "content": "同时和好几个人说话的时候，眼睛到底要怎样去看别人(╥ω╥`)  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895439}, {"id": 151849, "content": "如何机智地拒酒?", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897010}, {"id": 151338, "content": "大领导当着直属领导的面说我想提拔你到我这，你要不要来啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 325370}, {"id": 151343, "content": "如何自然地融入各种人事圈？", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892878}, {"id": 151602, "content": "遇到小人总在上司面前说你坏话让你很难升职怎么办？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895543}, {"id": 151858, "content": "怎样的方式沟通可以让同事和领导感觉舒适，不会反感？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897104}, {"id": 151603, "content": "当老板抢功或者暗示/纵容别人抢功的时候如何优雅体面地防御和反击？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880713}, {"id": 151859, "content": "新人该如何正确地向资质老的前辈请教", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755477}, {"id": 152115, "content": "从去年 7 月开始，你可能已经发现，在全国的很多肯德基、麦当劳餐厅里，已经没法让经理开出带公司名称抬头、甚至是普通的定额发票了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 20728}, {"id": 151348, "content": "有意见不知道怎么讲", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 372536}, {"id": 151604, "content": "老板抢功或者暗示/容忍他人抢功时如何优雅体面的防御/反击？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880713}, {"id": 151860, "content": "上级领导交代给你的工作恰好你因为某种不可推卸的原因必须拒绝，这样该怎么办？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897152}, {"id": 151605, "content": "不想加班，工作量大，该怎么说NO", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772283}, {"id": 151350, "content": "工作完成，在办公室无事可做。", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 372536}, {"id": 156472, "content": "暗恋好奇心日报的某个女编辑很久了 怎么不失优雅的表白", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898678}, {"id": 151353, "content": "如何区分有时要按制度走流程，有时又可以不按制度不走流程的事？", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 860854}]}